{"tid":809354,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"新同事出trip返黎，竟然無買手信比我地。。。。。","createTime":"2018-09-07T06:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T16:16:08.000Z","uid":36497,"like":58,"dislike":105,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"061a8fe870be361426ebf00194d38f8c359a29ca","tid":809354,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"FG新同事今日出完trip返到公司，大家都好welcome佢返黎（d野多到做唔哂，終於多一個人做d豬肉骨野）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁佢就跟manager去左台北3日2夜，我地都 expect佢應該會買d鳳梨穌 豬肉紙 太陽餅返黎啦，基本禮貌黎架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢返黎兩手空空，問佢點解無買手信，佢竟然話無時間（但佢只不過係幫手搬下行李，做下跑腿姐）！！<br />\n仲話下次一定會買返（食屎啦，你以為你仲有下一次咩)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反manager返黎就拎左3盒牛軋糖，2盒太陽餅比大家！根本係條友仔唔識人情細古／無錢買手信！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568d297615a1439030afad1d6cdadc5783813813","tid":809354,"uid":147001,"like":28,"dislike":7,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T06:06:40.000Z","msg":"個FG新同事係咪90後?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0c26e2f870413e439b7b695a8749ddbee1816f","tid":809354,"uid":55851,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T06:06:41.000Z","msg":"唔係話針對幾多十後，不過..."},{"pid":"b15c59084367c054f8aada8c0057b04c4c8ca503","tid":809354,"uid":65024,"like":62,"dislike":6,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T06:07:04.000Z","msg":"點解要買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481267589447ce8105b5964e42a655adf13d11d9","tid":809354,"uid":37733,"like":11,"dislike":9,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T06:07:08.000Z","msg":"以後俾多d粗重野佢做<br />\n等佢學識下咩野叫做人情細故啦"},{"pid":"f